column4: BlackRock CEO says Trump 'tax holiday' may do little for U.S. growth -CNBC
column5: NEW YORK  Jan 13 BlackRock Inc CEO Larry Fink on Friday criticized a policy backed by U.S. President-elect Donald Trump to entice U.S. companies to bring their swelling overseas cash piles home  saying a tax holiday may do little to boost growth.
